{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a two-story house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Downstairs was a different owner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had the upstairs, going through a stairway to her apartment-- beautiful, beautiful view.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her husband, under Russian occupation, committed suicide because she was considered capitalist wealthy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To Brody's standard, he was rich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had wholesale products, distributing to stores, and he was wealthy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were able to save some products in storage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And during Russian occupation, he was the capitalist, a [? candidate, ?] and his [INAUDIBLE] would have to be taken to be Siberia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was so afraid that they're going to come at night and take him to Siberia that he committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It came upon her to go down to the cellar and find him hung.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He hung himself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe he was-- I mean people go through all that, and they don't do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He went into such depression and fear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it came upon her to tell the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she was a very courageous woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She occupied that house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when the Germans came and they needed quarters, they wanted to evacuate her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She should remove-- move from her premises.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she begged them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She said, I'm going to clean your rooms and do all the chores for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So let me stay just in one room and in the kitchen with my children, which was a good deal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So she stayed on in her house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Trunzer occupied one of those rooms, beautiful rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I came to work for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So my chore was to clean his room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Schubert was her name-- Ethel Schubert.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She polished those parquet floors and did all the-- and did their laundry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But it was a whole upstairs, a whole floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She could not have done it alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
